reviewText:
This tape contains two features - Iron Man and Spiderman.  While this tape was released in 1985, the content was produced in 1966 and 1968.  You will either love or hate it.  I have seen it some many times since buying it in the early 90s - the high pitched theme song is "the" Iron Man song for me.  Quality is reasonable considering it is very low quality animation to start with.  If you are a die hard IronMan fan you will want this tape.

-1 star for having only 1/2 the tape for IronMan.
